00:31:18.300 --> 00:31:19.100 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:31:19.100 --> 00:31:21.830 align:middle line:90%


00:31:21.830 --> 00:31:25.400 align:middle line:84%
>> So, Andre, did you like
Minister Veneranda's lecture?

00:31:25.400 --> 00:31:28.790 align:middle line:84%
>> I could never imagine these
scenes or such impressive

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:29.730 align:middle line:90%
ideas.

00:31:29.730 --> 00:31:30.530 align:middle line:90%
>> I know.

00:31:30.530 --> 00:31:32.840 align:middle line:84%
There have been tough
times here in the hospital.

00:31:32.840 --> 00:31:35.690 align:middle line:84%
Now try to change your
thoughts, my friend.

00:31:35.690 --> 00:31:39.950 align:middle line:84%
>> Lucius, it's not easy going
through what I've been through.

00:31:39.950 --> 00:31:43.760 align:middle line:84%
>> You're recovering
depends on that too.

00:31:43.760 --> 00:31:46.520 align:middle line:90%
It's the law of synchrony.

00:31:46.520 --> 00:31:48.770 align:middle line:84%
>> You're saying that
if I get angry again,

00:31:48.770 --> 00:31:50.140 align:middle line:90%
I could go back to Umbral?

00:31:50.140 --> 00:31:51.710 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:31:51.710 --> 00:31:53.840 align:middle line:90%
>> You never know, Andre.

00:31:53.840 --> 00:31:57.500 align:middle line:84%
Our feelings and thoughts
decide where we will be.

00:31:57.500 --> 00:31:59.990 align:middle line:84%
>> Lucius, I need to
know about my family.

00:31:59.990 --> 00:32:01.820 align:middle line:90%
>> All in good time, remember?

00:32:01.820 --> 00:32:03.890 align:middle line:84%
>> They were really
suffering due to my disease.

00:32:03.890 --> 00:32:05.840 align:middle line:90%
>> Andre.

00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:08.810 align:middle line:84%
>> My relatives that had died
before me-- aren't they here?

00:32:08.810 --> 00:32:11.396 align:middle line:90%
My father, my-- my mo--

00:32:11.396 --> 00:32:12.650 align:middle line:90%
my, God.

00:32:12.650 --> 00:32:13.970 align:middle line:90%
>> So you do believe.

00:32:13.970 --> 00:32:16.905 align:middle line:84%
I thought you were one of those
people who say, I'm an atheist.

00:32:16.905 --> 00:32:17.705 align:middle line:90%
Thank God.

00:32:17.705 --> 00:32:20.390 align:middle line:90%


00:32:20.390 --> 00:32:22.490 align:middle line:90%
You'll know more bit by bit.

00:32:22.490 --> 00:32:23.960 align:middle line:90%
Just give time.

00:32:23.960 --> 00:32:25.160 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:32:25.160 --> 00:32:26.630 align:middle line:90%
Let's take the arrow bus.

00:32:26.630 --> 00:32:28.730 align:middle line:90%
>> Wait, take what?

00:32:28.730 --> 00:32:30.130 align:middle line:84%
Where does this
energy come from?

00:32:30.130 --> 00:32:33.260 align:middle line:84%
>> Soon engineers will
reincarnate and take with them

00:32:33.260 --> 00:32:35.315 align:middle line:84%
technology such as this
with them to the planet.

00:32:35.315 --> 00:32:36.440 align:middle line:90%
>> What kind of technology?

00:32:36.440 --> 00:32:38.480 align:middle line:84%
>> How do you use
magnetism for instance.

00:32:38.480 --> 00:32:41.300 align:middle line:84%
It's life on Earth that's
a copy from here, Andre.

00:32:41.300 --> 00:32:45.230 align:middle line:84%
To be born, die, and be reborn
so many times, as many times

00:32:45.230 --> 00:32:47.220 align:middle line:90%
as necessary.

00:32:47.220 --> 00:32:49.820 align:middle line:90%
It's the law.

00:32:49.820 --> 00:32:52.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey, stop reading my mind.

00:32:52.910 --> 00:32:54.270 align:middle line:90%
>> You're much better.

00:32:54.270 --> 00:32:56.270 align:middle line:90%
>> I don't know why.

00:32:56.270 --> 00:32:58.970 align:middle line:84%
>> Does the one who keeps
complaining have time to smile?

00:32:58.970 --> 00:33:03.260 align:middle line:90%
>> Dr. Andre, what a surprise.

00:33:03.260 --> 00:33:04.280 align:middle line:90%
Oh, my God.

00:33:04.280 --> 00:33:06.830 align:middle line:90%
What a pleasure to see you here.

00:33:06.830 --> 00:33:08.780 align:middle line:90%
You don't remember me, do you?

00:33:08.780 --> 00:33:10.070 align:middle line:90%
I'm Amelia.

00:33:10.070 --> 00:33:12.470 align:middle line:84%
I was always your last
patient of your day.

00:33:12.470 --> 00:33:15.640 align:middle line:84%
It was me and my husband and
you never charged anything.

00:33:15.640 --> 00:33:16.820 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yes.

00:33:16.820 --> 00:33:19.080 align:middle line:90%
You had the severe headaches.

00:33:19.080 --> 00:33:21.140 align:middle line:90%
>> Stomach aches.

00:33:21.140 --> 00:33:22.220 align:middle line:90%
>> Sure.

00:33:22.220 --> 00:33:23.060 align:middle line:90%
Got better?

00:33:23.060 --> 00:33:24.140 align:middle line:90%
>> I died, right?

00:33:24.140 --> 00:33:25.310 align:middle line:90%
So I got better.

00:33:25.310 --> 00:33:26.850 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:33:26.850 --> 00:33:27.650 align:middle line:90%


00:33:27.650 --> 00:33:28.550 align:middle line:90%
[DEEP SIGH]

00:33:28.550 --> 00:33:30.290 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm waiting for Anternor.

00:33:30.290 --> 00:33:32.300 align:middle line:90%
He was full of diseases.

00:33:32.300 --> 00:33:33.350 align:middle line:90%
Do you remember?

00:33:33.350 --> 00:33:36.860 align:middle line:90%
But he simply does not die.

00:33:36.860 --> 00:33:37.940 align:middle line:90%
>> Ma'am, I am sorry.

00:33:37.940 --> 00:33:40.220 align:middle line:90%
But Dr. Andre is a newcomer.

00:33:40.220 --> 00:33:43.610 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm sure you came straight to
this place and you didn't have

00:33:43.610 --> 00:33:46.490 align:middle line:84%
to stay in that
horrible other place.

00:33:46.490 --> 00:33:48.770 align:middle line:90%
You're a good man.

00:33:48.770 --> 00:33:51.785 align:middle line:84%
I'm certain you came
straight to Astral City.

00:33:51.785 --> 00:33:54.800 align:middle line:90%


00:33:54.800 --> 00:33:58.310 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Andre, once you're all set
and start seeing your patients,

00:33:58.310 --> 00:34:00.020 align:middle line:90%
I'll come pay you a visit.

00:34:00.020 --> 00:34:01.275 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you, Aurelia.

00:34:01.275 --> 00:34:02.075 align:middle line:90%
>> Amelia.

00:34:02.075 --> 00:34:05.230 align:middle line:90%


00:34:05.230 --> 00:34:07.220 align:middle line:90%
>> Amelia.

00:34:07.220 --> 00:34:08.600 align:middle line:90%
[SIGHS]

00:34:08.600 --> 00:34:12.883 align:middle line:84%
>> In situations like this,
it's better not to say anything.

00:34:12.883 --> 00:34:13.925 align:middle line:90%
>> Thanks for the advice.

00:34:13.925 --> 00:34:16.465 align:middle line:90%


00:34:16.465 --> 00:34:17.465 align:middle line:90%
You could be a minister.

00:34:17.465 --> 00:34:22.340 align:middle line:90%


00:34:22.340 --> 00:34:25.530 align:middle line:84%
>> All right, I will tell you
a bit of this place's history.

00:34:25.530 --> 00:34:28.100 align:middle line:84%
But pay attention because
I'll only tell you this once.

00:34:28.100 --> 00:34:28.900 align:middle line:90%
Deal?

00:34:28.900 --> 00:34:31.580 align:middle line:90%


00:34:31.580 --> 00:34:33.754 align:middle line:90%
>> Deal.

00:34:33.754 --> 00:34:35.239 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:34:35.239 --> 00:34:38.130 align:middle line:90%


00:34:38.130 --> 00:34:42.120 align:middle line:84%
>> First this one, the
Edification Ministry.

00:34:42.120 --> 00:34:44.880 align:middle line:84%
Astral City was built
in the 16th century.

00:34:44.880 --> 00:34:46.650 align:middle line:90%
And everything here has a why.

00:34:46.650 --> 00:34:49.110 align:middle line:90%
You'll be able to realize later.

00:34:49.110 --> 00:34:51.840 align:middle line:84%
There we have the
Divine Union, which

00:34:51.840 --> 00:34:54.510 align:middle line:84%
deals with issues
of superior levels,

00:34:54.510 --> 00:34:56.234 align:middle line:84%
along with the
Governor's Palace.

00:34:56.234 --> 00:34:59.940 align:middle line:90%


00:34:59.940 --> 00:35:03.750 align:middle line:84%
These are the enlightenment
and communications buildings

00:35:03.750 --> 00:35:07.080 align:middle line:84%
where research is done and
messages to families on Earth

00:35:07.080 --> 00:35:09.750 align:middle line:90%
are sent, among other things.

00:35:09.750 --> 00:35:12.490 align:middle line:90%


00:35:12.490 --> 00:35:14.890 align:middle line:84%
You are at the
Regeneration Ministry,

00:35:14.890 --> 00:35:19.210 align:middle line:84%
right beside the
Reincarnation Pavilion.

00:35:19.210 --> 00:35:21.430 align:middle line:84%
Which I must confess,
I'm not very fond of.

00:35:21.430 --> 00:35:24.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Why?

00:35:24.030 --> 00:35:25.581 align:middle line:90%
>> You'll know one day.

00:35:25.581 --> 00:35:27.790 align:middle line:90%
[DEEP SIGH]

00:35:27.790 --> 00:35:30.190 align:middle line:84%
In each of its six
points, the main square

00:35:30.190 --> 00:35:32.750 align:middle line:90%
