00:35:32.750 --> 00:35:36.860 align:middle line:10%
There are 72 ministers
in this city, Andre,

00:35:36.860 --> 00:35:39.082 align:middle line:10%
just like God's breaths.

00:35:39.082 --> 00:35:41.974 align:middle line:90%
[UPBEAT MUSIC]

00:35:41.974 --> 00:35:42.938 align:middle line:90%


00:35:42.938 --> 00:35:44.866 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:35:44.866 --> 00:35:49.030 align:middle line:90%


00:35:49.030 --> 00:35:51.880 align:middle line:84%
>> I was faced with
a new paradigm.

00:35:51.880 --> 00:35:55.030 align:middle line:84%
I saw people leaving
to be reborn on Earth

00:35:55.030 --> 00:35:56.650 align:middle line:90%
but leaving the sadness behind.

00:35:56.650 --> 00:35:59.950 align:middle line:90%


00:35:59.950 --> 00:36:04.600 align:middle line:84%
Little by little, I started
to make sense of everything.

00:36:04.600 --> 00:36:08.320 align:middle line:84%
Astral City was the
real life and Earth

00:36:08.320 --> 00:36:09.565 align:middle line:90%
was only a mere passage.

00:36:09.565 --> 00:36:12.360 align:middle line:90%


00:36:12.360 --> 00:36:14.286 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:36:14.286 --> 00:36:16.680 align:middle line:90%


00:36:16.680 --> 00:36:17.560 align:middle line:90%
>> You won't make it.

00:36:17.560 --> 00:36:20.100 align:middle line:90%


00:36:20.100 --> 00:36:22.476 align:middle line:90%
>> So how do you know?

00:36:22.476 --> 00:36:27.030 align:middle line:84%
>> I've been lost many
times on those tracks,

00:36:27.030 --> 00:36:29.400 align:middle line:90%
unless that's what you want.

00:36:29.400 --> 00:36:30.610 align:middle line:90%
>> I want to see my family.

00:36:30.610 --> 00:36:31.818 align:middle line:90%
Do you think that's possible?

00:36:31.818 --> 00:36:34.590 align:middle line:90%


00:36:34.590 --> 00:36:37.770 align:middle line:90%
>> One day, who knows?

00:36:37.770 --> 00:36:39.690 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:36:39.690 --> 00:36:44.190 align:middle line:84%
>> But I was still the same man,
attached to my own mistakes,

00:36:44.190 --> 00:36:46.350 align:middle line:84%
to my selfishness,
and to my past.

00:36:46.350 --> 00:36:51.820 align:middle line:90%


00:36:51.820 --> 00:36:53.850 align:middle line:90%
>> Doctor.

00:36:53.850 --> 00:36:54.690 align:middle line:90%
Doctor Andre.

00:36:54.690 --> 00:36:57.875 align:middle line:90%


00:36:57.875 --> 00:36:58.675 align:middle line:90%
Dr. Andre.

00:36:58.675 --> 00:37:03.230 align:middle line:90%


00:37:03.230 --> 00:37:04.720 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:37:04.720 --> 00:37:21.880 align:middle line:90%


00:37:21.880 --> 00:37:23.380 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm sorry.

00:37:23.380 --> 00:37:24.360 align:middle line:90%
May I interrupt?

00:37:24.360 --> 00:37:26.290 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, of course.

00:37:26.290 --> 00:37:29.770 align:middle line:84%
You know, I'm going to have to
do much more research anyway.

00:37:29.770 --> 00:37:31.190 align:middle line:90%
Pleasure, Emmanuel.

00:37:31.190 --> 00:37:31.990 align:middle line:90%
>> Hi.

00:37:31.990 --> 00:37:32.815 align:middle line:90%
I'm Andre Luiz.

00:37:32.815 --> 00:37:35.780 align:middle line:90%


00:37:35.780 --> 00:37:39.190 align:middle line:84%
