00:37:41.660 --> 00:37:45.370 align:middle line:84%
tell them that I'm
here, that I miss them.

00:37:45.370 --> 00:37:47.860 align:middle line:84%
Actually, I have so much
to say that I don't even

00:37:47.860 --> 00:37:48.970 align:middle line:90%
know where to start.

00:37:48.970 --> 00:37:51.790 align:middle line:90%
>> You start right here.

00:37:51.790 --> 00:37:55.060 align:middle line:84%
Did someone explain to you
how our communication ministry

00:37:55.060 --> 00:37:56.350 align:middle line:90%
works?

00:37:56.350 --> 00:37:59.830 align:middle line:84%
You can choose the technology,
enter from the future

00:37:59.830 --> 00:38:02.950 align:middle line:90%
or from the past.

00:38:02.950 --> 00:38:04.300 align:middle line:90%
>> The oldest.

00:38:04.300 --> 00:38:05.950 align:middle line:90%
>> That I know, please.

00:38:05.950 --> 00:38:06.820 align:middle line:90%
>> Excuse me.

00:38:06.820 --> 00:38:07.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Mr. Emmanuel.

00:38:07.620 --> 00:38:11.180 align:middle line:90%


00:38:11.180 --> 00:38:14.120 align:middle line:84%
