a lot after I left.

00:38:16.230 --> 00:38:19.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Jonas, your mother won't
suffer anymore after she knows

00:38:19.310 --> 00:38:22.820 align:middle line:84%
you're very well, with so much
that you've been telling us

00:38:22.820 --> 00:38:23.990 align:middle line:90%
here.

00:38:23.990 --> 00:38:25.100 align:middle line:90%
>> And what do we do now?

00:38:25.100 --> 00:38:26.840 align:middle line:90%
>> Now, you wait.

00:38:26.840 --> 00:38:30.000 align:middle line:84%
I'll let know as soon as you
have permission to speak.

00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:32.390 align:middle line:84%
We have a reincarnated
brother who

00:38:32.390 --> 00:38:37.280 align:middle line:84%
