the messages that we can send.

00:38:37.280 --> 00:38:39.845 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you very much.

00:38:39.845 --> 00:38:41.560 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:38:41.560 --> 00:38:47.930 align:middle line:90%


00:38:47.930 --> 00:38:50.460 align:middle line:84%
>> Andre, finding it
hard to start writing?

00:38:50.460 --> 00:38:51.260 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:38:51.260 --> 00:38:52.060 align:middle line:90%
That's it.

00:38:52.060 --> 00:38:53.480 align:middle line:90%
>> It's always like this.

00:38:53.480 --> 00:38:55.910 align:middle line:84%
You can look for brother
Genicio at the Ministry.

00:38:55.910 --> 00:38:58.620 align:middle line:84%
You'll find what you're
looking for there.

00:38:58.620 --> 00:38:59.420 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:38:59.420 --> 00:39:10.575 align:middle line:90%


00:39:10.575 --> 00:39:13.425 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:39:13.425 --> 00:39:17.990 align:middle line:90%


00:39:17.990 --> 00:39:18.790 align:middle line:90%
>> How are you?

00:39:18.790 --> 00:39:22.276 align:middle line:90%


00:39:22.276 --> 00:39:23.658 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:39:23.658 --> 00:39:33.780 align:middle line:90%


00:39:33.780 --> 00:39:34.860 align:middle line:90%
>> Minister, excuse me.

00:39:34.860 --> 00:39:36.720 align:middle line:90%
May we talk in private?

00:39:36.720 --> 00:39:39.090 align:middle line:90%
>> Forgive our brother.

00:39:39.090 --> 00:39:41.400 align:middle line:84%
After them, I will
certainly give you

00:39:41.400 --> 00:39:42.840 align:middle line:90%
the support that you need.

00:39:42.840 --> 00:39:44.550 align:middle line:90%
>> But I won't be long.

00:39:44.550 --> 00:39:46.620 align:middle line:90%
>> As well as them.

00:39:46.620 --> 00:39:48.210 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:39:48.210 --> 00:39:53.540 align:middle line:90%


00:39:53.540 --> 00:39:54.850 align:middle line:90%
>> I am sorry.

00:39:54.850 --> 00:39:55.650 align:middle line:90%
Excuse me.

00:39:55.650 --> 00:39:59.816 align:middle line:90%


00:39:59.816 --> 00:40:00.785 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:40:00.785 --> 00:40:13.530 align:middle line:90%


00:40:13.530 --> 00:40:15.300 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:40:15.300 --> 00:40:38.940 align:middle line:90%


00:40:38.940 --> 00:40:39.975 align:middle line:90%
>> Andre Luiz.

00:40:39.975 --> 00:40:47.272 align:middle line:90%


00:40:47.272 --> 00:40:49.224 align:middle line:90%
[SIGHS DEEPLY]

00:40:49.224 --> 00:40:51.680 align:middle line:90%


00:40:51.680 --> 00:40:54.050 align:middle line:90%
I see you in prayers.

00:40:54.050 --> 00:40:55.100 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you, Minister.

00:40:55.100 --> 00:40:56.000 align:middle line:90%
Thank you very much.

00:40:56.000 --> 00:40:59.870 align:middle line:90%


00:40:59.870 --> 00:41:00.875 align:middle line:90%
>> Ladies first.

00:41:00.875 --> 00:41:03.750 align:middle line:90%


00:41:03.750 --> 00:41:05.430 align:middle line:90%
What can I do for you, ma'am?

00:41:05.430 --> 00:41:09.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Minister Genicio, I need
to see my children on Earth.

00:41:09.420 --> 00:41:12.610 align:middle line:84%
The poor things are suffering so
much because of me being here.

00:41:12.610 --> 00:41:14.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Even though the family
ties are not broken with

00:41:14.880 --> 00:41:22.680 align:middle line:84%
