00:41:27.700 --> 00:41:30.000 align:middle line:90%
>> If you mean work, well, none.

00:41:30.000 --> 00:41:33.090 align:middle line:90%


00:41:33.090 --> 00:41:35.430 align:middle line:84%
>> How long have you been
at the colony, ma'am?

00:41:35.430 --> 00:41:37.900 align:middle line:90%
>> Six painful years.

00:41:37.900 --> 00:41:40.830 align:middle line:84%
>> And during all this time
you haven't found anything that

00:41:40.830 --> 00:41:42.690 align:middle line:90%
piqued your interest?

00:41:42.690 --> 00:41:44.610 align:middle line:90%
>> I've never had to work.

00:41:44.610 --> 00:41:49.380 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, ma'am, Astral City
has offers for you from food

00:41:49.380 --> 00:41:53.790 align:middle line:84%
factories to visiting services
to friends in recovery.

00:41:53.790 --> 00:41:57.030 align:middle line:84%
>> It's all a bit
tiresome, don't you think?

00:41:57.030 --> 00:42:00.600 align:middle line:84%
>> Nothing worth
having comes easy.

00:42:00.600 --> 00:42:02.160 align:middle line:90%
>> I've been told.

00:42:02.160 --> 00:42:04.530 align:middle line:84%
>> Look at your
own acts, sister,

00:42:04.530 --> 00:42:09.114 align:middle line:84%
