01:28:59.584 --> 01:29:03.063 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:29:03.063 --> 01:29:04.554 align:middle line:90%


01:29:04.554 --> 01:29:08.530 align:middle line:90%
[FAINT GROWLS]

01:29:08.530 --> 01:29:11.015 align:middle line:90%
[INTENSE MUSIC]

01:29:11.015 --> 01:29:13.500 align:middle line:90%
[YELLING, MOANING]

01:29:13.500 --> 01:29:36.362 align:middle line:90%


01:29:36.362 --> 01:29:38.847 align:middle line:90%
[SOBBING]

01:29:38.847 --> 01:29:48.787 align:middle line:90%


01:29:48.787 --> 01:29:50.775 align:middle line:90%
[THUNDER CLAPS]

01:29:50.775 --> 01:30:08.170 align:middle line:90%


01:30:08.170 --> 01:30:12.382 align:middle line:90%
[GROWLING]

01:30:12.382 --> 01:30:14.405 align:middle line:90%
[INTENSE MUSIC]

01:30:14.405 --> 01:30:27.275 align:middle line:90%


01:30:27.275 --> 01:30:29.255 align:middle line:90%
[PEACEFUL MUSIC]

01:30:29.255 --> 01:30:41.140 align:middle line:90%


01:30:41.140 --> 01:30:43.300 align:middle line:90%
>> Mom?

01:30:43.300 --> 01:30:45.250 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm so glad you
made it, Clarice.

01:30:45.250 --> 01:30:46.780 align:middle line:90%
>> How are you?

01:30:46.780 --> 01:30:47.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Fine.

01:30:47.650 --> 01:30:50.800 align:middle line:84%
I was a little frightened,
but I'm all right.

01:30:50.800 --> 01:30:52.670 align:middle line:90%
>> Good.

01:30:52.670 --> 01:30:55.010 align:middle line:10%
You know, I thought a
lot about dad today.

01:30:55.010 --> 01:30:56.900 align:middle line:10%
>> Your father?

01:30:56.900 --> 01:31:00.045 align:middle line:90%
Sweetheart, don't tell me that.

01:31:00.045 --> 01:31:00.920 align:middle line:90%
>> What's wrong, mom?

01:31:00.920 --> 01:31:04.760 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm already suffering and you
bring up something so gloomy.

01:31:04.760 --> 01:31:07.250 align:middle line:84%
It's not a good time to
speak about your father.

01:31:07.250 --> 01:31:08.180 align:middle line:90%
Agreed?

01:31:08.180 --> 01:31:10.380 align:middle line:84%
>> Sorry, I just wanted
to tell you how I felt.

01:31:10.380 --> 01:31:14.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Clarice, dear, your
father is no longer with us.

01:31:14.880 --> 01:31:16.800 align:middle line:90%
I know that it was painful.

01:31:16.800 --> 01:31:18.950 align:middle line:90%
It was for me too.

01:31:18.950 --> 01:31:22.640 align:middle line:84%
But that's all in the past and
the past is done and buried.

01:31:22.640 --> 01:31:24.680 align:middle line:90%
>> Who's at rest?

01:31:24.680 --> 01:31:27.080 align:middle line:84%
>> Mom doesn't want
me talking about dad.

01:31:27.080 --> 01:31:29.660 align:middle line:84%
>> But what good is it
to remember him, Clarice?

01:31:29.660 --> 01:31:30.710 align:middle line:90%
>> I just miss him.

01:31:30.710 --> 01:31:33.750 align:middle line:90%


01:31:33.750 --> 01:31:35.000 align:middle line:90%
>> I don't know if I miss him.

01:31:35.000 --> 01:31:39.130 align:middle line:90%


01:31:39.130 --> 01:31:40.778 align:middle line:90%
I wish I did.

01:31:40.778 --> 01:31:42.820 align:middle line:84%
>> I read in a book that
people don't really die.

01:31:42.820 --> 01:31:44.112 align:middle line:90%
>> Clarice, dear, please don't.

01:31:44.112 --> 01:31:45.190 align:middle line:90%
>> This is nonsense, sis.

01:31:45.190 --> 01:31:46.270 align:middle line:90%
Quit being a fool.

01:31:46.270 --> 01:31:48.220 align:middle line:84%
Science can disprove
these kinds of fraud.

01:31:48.220 --> 01:31:49.300 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

01:31:49.300 --> 01:31:51.100 align:middle line:90%
>> You sound just like dad.

01:31:51.100 --> 01:31:52.270 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

01:31:52.270 --> 01:31:55.033 align:middle line:84%
>> Maybe that's why I
decided to become a doctor.

01:31:55.033 --> 01:31:56.965 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:31:56.965 --> 01:32:02.278 align:middle line:90%


01:32:02.278 --> 01:32:04.898 align:middle line:90%
[DEEPLY EXHALES]

01:32:04.898 --> 01:32:06.810 align:middle line:90%
>> How's Ernesto?

01:32:06.810 --> 01:32:08.430 align:middle line:90%
>> Come, let's go see.

01:32:08.430 --> 01:32:19.890 align:middle line:90%


01:32:19.890 --> 01:32:21.075 align:middle line:90%
>> Mom, I'm home.

01:32:21.075 --> 01:32:35.806 align:middle line:90%


01:32:35.806 --> 01:32:37.288 align:middle line:90%
[PLAYING PIANO]

01:32:37.288 --> 01:33:03.490 align:middle line:90%


01:33:03.490 --> 01:33:04.820 align:middle line:90%
>> Maria Clara?

01:33:04.820 --> 01:33:06.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Hi, Clarice.

01:33:06.910 --> 01:33:09.580 align:middle line:84%
>> Who taught you the
song you're playing?

01:33:09.580 --> 01:33:10.460 align:middle line:90%
>> I don't know.

01:33:10.460 --> 01:33:11.890 align:middle line:90%
I just sat and played.

01:33:11.890 --> 01:33:14.710 align:middle line:90%
>> Do you know how it goes?

01:33:14.710 --> 01:33:16.198 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

01:33:16.198 --> 01:33:18.154 align:middle line:90%
[PLAYING PIANO]

01:33:18.154 --> 01:33:36.740 align:middle line:90%


01:33:36.740 --> 01:33:39.770 align:middle line:84%
>> I learned to play it when
I was your age, you know?

01:33:39.770 --> 01:33:42.710 align:middle line:90%
Dad loved to watch me play.

01:33:42.710 --> 01:33:45.130 align:middle line:90%
>> How was he, Clarice?

01:33:45.130 --> 01:33:50.730 align:middle line:84%
>> Ah, he was a very
good man, very busy,

01:33:50.730 --> 01:33:54.210 align:middle line:90%
never had much time for us.

01:33:54.210 --> 01:33:56.430 align:middle line:90%
He was tough, stern.

01:33:56.430 --> 01:33:58.170 align:middle line:84%
I never saw him
crying, you know?

01:33:58.170 --> 01:33:59.610 align:middle line:90%
>> But boys don't cry.

01:33:59.610 --> 01:34:00.450 align:middle line:90%
>> That's right.

01:34:00.450 --> 01:34:02.520 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

01:34:02.520 --> 01:34:05.430 align:middle line:84%
I think he just
did what he thought

01:34:05.430 --> 01:34:06.945 align:middle line:90%
people expected him to do.

01:34:06.945 --> 01:34:09.590 align:middle line:90%


01:34:09.590 --> 01:34:12.020 align:middle line:84%
But he loved us, and that's
what's important, right?

01:34:12.020 --> 01:34:14.460 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, but I don't
understand anything.

01:34:14.460 --> 01:34:15.260 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

01:34:15.260 --> 01:34:17.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, you don't have to.

01:34:17.030 --> 01:34:20.790 align:middle line:84%
If one day things are
the way I think they are,

01:34:20.790 --> 01:34:23.205 align:middle line:90%
we'll meet again.

01:34:23.205 --> 01:34:24.005 align:middle line:90%
>> I hope so.

01:34:24.005 --> 01:34:27.190 align:middle line:90%


01:34:27.190 --> 01:34:29.824 align:middle line:90%
>> Come on, play.

01:34:29.824 --> 01:34:32.812 align:middle line:90%
[PLAYING PIANO]

01:34:32.812 --> 01:34:43.768 align:middle line:90%


01:34:43.768 --> 01:34:47.254 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:34:47.254 --> 01:36:30.390 align:middle line:90%


01:36:30.390 --> 01:36:32.226 align:middle line:90%
>> How lovely.

01:36:32.226 --> 01:36:34.170 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

01:36:34.170 --> 01:36:36.120 align:middle line:90%


01:36:36.120 --> 01:36:40.380 align:middle line:84%
>> Life doesn't end and death
is a dark game of illusions.

01:36:40.380 --> 01:36:45.180 align:middle line:84%
Closing our bodily eyes
doesn't decide our fate.

01:36:45.180 --> 01:36:50.070 align:middle line:84%
It's necessary to go through
our own drama or our own comedy

01:36:50.070 --> 01:36:54.600 align:middle line:84%
so we can cross all the paths
of our spiritual evolution.

01:36:54.600 --> 01:36:59.040 align:middle line:84%
Only then will we find the
waters of the divine ocean.

01:36:59.040 --> 01:37:01.800 align:middle line:10%
Existence is an act, a body--

01:37:01.800 --> 01:37:03.750 align:middle line:10%
a vessel, a century--

01:37:03.750 --> 01:37:05.070 align:middle line:10%
a day.

01:37:05.070 --> 01:37:08.310 align:middle line:84%
And death-- death is
the renewed breath.

01:37:08.310 --> 01:37:12.090 align:middle line:90%


01:37:12.090 --> 01:37:14.312 align:middle line:90%
>> Did you know of this text?

01:37:14.312 --> 01:37:16.072 align:middle line:90%
[DEEP SIGH]

01:37:16.072 --> 01:37:18.280 align:middle line:84%
>> I never could have imagined
the awakening could be

01:37:18.280 --> 01:37:20.750 align:middle line:90%
so intense.

01:37:20.750 --> 01:37:24.820 align:middle line:84%
>> But I won't suffer
with the idea of eternity.

01:37:24.820 --> 01:37:27.055 align:middle line:84%
>> It's always a good
time to start over.

01:37:27.055 --> 01:37:31.530 align:middle line:90%


01:37:31.530 --> 01:37:35.780 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, the divine voice
that speaks in the sanctuary

01:37:35.780 --> 01:37:42.020 align:middle line:84%
of my soul is only
forgiveness and love.

01:37:42.020 --> 01:37:49.255 align:middle line:90%
Zelia, forgive me.

01:37:49.255 --> 01:37:50.752 align:middle line:90%
[CHOIR SINGING]

01:37:50.752 --> 01:37:55.742 align:middle line:90%


01:37:55.742 --> 01:37:57.738 align:middle line:90%
[COUGHING]

01:37:57.738 --> 01:37:58.435 align:middle line:90%


01:37:58.435 --> 01:37:59.235 align:middle line:90%
[GASPS]

01:37:59.235 --> 01:38:22.190 align:middle line:90%


01:38:22.190 --> 01:38:24.245 align:middle line:90%
>> Godspeed, Doctor Andre.

01:38:24.245 --> 01:38:29.590 align:middle line:90%


01:38:29.590 --> 01:38:32.209 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you, Ismalia.

01:38:32.209 --> 01:38:34.181 align:middle line:90%
[CHOIR SINGING]

01:38:34.181 --> 01:39:03.761 align:middle line:90%


01:39:03.761 --> 01:39:07.270 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

01:39:07.270 --> 01:39:10.150 align:middle line:90%
>> Ernesto?

01:39:10.150 --> 01:39:10.950 align:middle line:90%
My God.

01:39:10.950 --> 01:39:13.510 align:middle line:90%


01:39:13.510 --> 01:39:16.490 align:middle line:90%
Ernesto, wake up.

01:39:16.490 --> 01:39:20.000 align:middle line:84%
No, for the love of God,
don't do this to me, Ernesto.

01:39:20.000 --> 01:39:21.200 align:middle line:90%
Ernesto!

01:39:21.200 --> 01:39:22.970 align:middle line:90%
Just breathe, Ernesto.

01:39:22.970 --> 01:39:24.000 align:middle line:90%
Please breathe.

01:39:24.000 --> 01:39:24.800 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm sick.

01:39:24.800 --> 01:39:27.080 align:middle line:90%
I'm not dead, Zelia.

01:39:27.080 --> 01:39:28.370 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, for heaven's sake.

01:39:28.370 --> 01:39:30.770 align:middle line:90%
You scared me.

01:39:30.770 --> 01:39:32.240 align:middle line:90%
[EXHALES]

01:39:32.240 --> 01:39:35.680 align:middle line:90%


01:39:35.680 --> 01:39:37.060 align:middle line:90%
>> You're feeling better.

01:39:37.060 --> 01:39:40.360 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, I'm so much better now.

01:39:40.360 --> 01:39:45.610 align:middle line:84%
You know, I dreamt of a
man, a very friendly man.

01:39:45.610 --> 01:39:49.180 align:middle line:84%
And he asked me to
drink some water.

01:39:49.180 --> 01:39:54.430 align:middle line:84%
And I think I actually drank
the whole jug last night.

01:39:54.430 --> 01:39:56.930 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:39:56.930 --> 01:40:01.930 align:middle line:90%


01:40:01.930 --> 01:40:02.860 align:middle line:90%
Ah, come here.

01:40:02.860 --> 01:40:05.200 align:middle line:90%
Sweetheart, come here.

01:40:05.200 --> 01:40:10.680 align:middle line:84%
Oh, my sweetheart,
my sweetheart.

01:40:10.680 --> 01:40:14.458 align:middle line:84%
I'm not leaving you
any time soon, OK?

01:40:14.458 --> 01:40:15.374 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

01:40:15.374 --> 01:40:22.612 align:middle line:90%


01:40:22.612 --> 01:40:24.516 align:middle line:90%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

01:40:24.516 --> 01:40:32.367 align:middle line:90%


01:40:32.367 --> 01:40:33.858 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:40:33.858 --> 01:40:44.295 align:middle line:90%


01:40:44.295 --> 01:40:46.283 align:middle line:90%
[VOCALIZING]

01:40:46.283 --> 01:41:41.050 align:middle line:90%


01:41:41.050 --> 01:41:44.470 align:middle line:84%
>> Every time a citizen from
Astral City returns from a very

01:41:44.470 --> 01:41:48.830 align:middle line:84%
well-accomplished mission, they
must be received by everyone

01:41:48.830 --> 01:41:51.410 align:middle line:90%
with much love and care.

01:41:51.410 --> 01:41:54.590 align:middle line:90%
Welcome back to our city, Andre.

01:41:54.590 --> 01:41:56.330 align:middle line:84%
>> Thank you for
everything, minister.

01:41:56.330 --> 01:41:57.130 align:middle line:90%
Tobias.

01:41:57.130 --> 01:42:00.040 align:middle line:84%
>> We might have an opening
in the Samaritans group.

01:42:00.040 --> 01:42:02.050 align:middle line:90%
>> Do you think I can?

01:42:02.050 --> 01:42:03.580 align:middle line:84%
>> If that's what
you want, why not?

01:42:03.580 --> 01:42:06.670 align:middle line:84%
>> But we can't forget the
work at the Chambers, right?

01:42:06.670 --> 01:42:08.490 align:middle line:84%
>> The work, always
the work, Andre.

01:42:08.490 --> 01:42:09.490 align:middle line:90%
>> You're right, Tobias.

01:42:09.490 --> 01:42:10.490 align:middle line:90%
>> What about the books?

01:42:10.490 --> 01:42:13.000 align:middle line:90%


01:42:13.000 --> 01:42:16.060 align:middle line:84%
Our friend on Earth
would love to meet you.

01:42:16.060 --> 01:42:17.860 align:middle line:90%
>> And who is it?

01:42:17.860 --> 01:42:20.950 align:middle line:84%
>> You can call him
Chico, just Chico.

01:42:20.950 --> 01:42:22.574 align:middle line:90%
>> God bless him.

01:42:22.574 --> 01:42:24.502 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:42:24.502 --> 01:42:33.680 align:middle line:90%


01:42:33.680 --> 01:42:37.340 align:middle line:84%
>> Andre Luiz continues his work
at the colony in Astral City

01:42:37.340 --> 01:42:38.375 align:middle line:90%
until this day.

01:42:38.375 --> 01:42:41.690 align:middle line:90%


01:42:41.690 --> 01:42:44.840 align:middle line:84%
He wrote 16 books with
the psychic, Chico Xavier,

01:42:44.840 --> 01:42:47.165 align:middle line:84%
about the life in
the spiritual world.

01:42:47.165 --> 01:42:52.260 align:middle line:90%


01:42:52.260 --> 01:42:56.220 align:middle line:84%
To Chico Xavier, Andre
Luiz, and to the inhabitants

01:42:56.220 --> 01:42:57.255 align:middle line:90%
of Astral City.

01:42:57.255 --> 01:43:04.310 align:middle line:90%


01:43:04.310 --> 01:43:07.610 align:middle line:84%
Based on the works
of Chico Xavier.

01:43:07.610 --> 01:43:09.760 align:middle line:90%
